      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "1. Your flying saucer crashed on the worst planet.\r\n2. You must signal
    the Rescue Mission\r\n3. The tablet shows a sign that needs to be drawn in a
    corn field to give a signal\r\n4. Use cornTool for drawing\r\n\u2014 LMB \u2014
    Trample the Corn\r\n\u2014 RMB \u2014 Raise the Corn\r\n\u2014 L \u2014 Flashlight\r\n5.
    Beware of the Rednecks"
